casebody.data:
DISCOVER BANK, Plaintiff,
v.
Nick BAVISHI, Defendant-Petitioner. C-681 September Term 2017
080430 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 26, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005014-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
